00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:52,660
What? How come?

328
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:55,560
Because ghosts don't exist.

329
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:02,260
It's all illusions.

330
00:20:02,260 --> 00:20:03,660
A strange figure in the window

