345
00:20:47,760 --> 00:20:50,460
Are you talking about me?

346
00:20:50,460 --> 00:20:52,560
That's not possible.

347
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:54,060
I checked it out right away back then,

348
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:57,660
